data.description: Dreaming of that wonderful place to call home...you know the place...the home that checks all the boxes....well look no further...your wish list is about to become reality. This remarkabe Ranch has exactly what you want and some extras. The covered front porch with ceiling fans is just the place for summer sitting, from there you will stroll through the living/dining room combo thats designed for great entertaining, oversized family room w/FP makes movie night with friends & family so much fun theres 4 bedrooms & 3 full baths, the Primary suite has full bath and a outstanding view of the lake, stylish kitchen & laundry room top off the inside of this home, Backyard is breathtaking, wrap around deck is just the place to relax and take in the views, beautiful garden areas, walkway that leads you to the lake and lets not forget the 2 car garage with AC, work shed with power & full home generator. This home is where family will love to gather, memories will be made and dreams come true.
